{"tid":2181051,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"懶理湯漢家書警告 韋格光神父講道：港人享更多自由民主夢碎","createTime":"2020-08-30T10:19:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T11:59:34.000Z","uid":240362,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4a15c8562c1a98f928d796680eae5b74e8659daa","tid":2181051,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T10:19:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200830/4VAGV3HUWRGZJDJQX33HBT4JEA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200830%2F4VAGV3HUWRGZJDJQX33HBT4JEA%2F&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoP5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=ecda1733\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200830%2F4VAGV3HUWRGZJDJQX33HBT4JEA%2F&h=abe8ef52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200830/4VAGV3HUWRGZJDJQX33HBT4JEA/</a><br />\n<br />\n天主教香港教區宗座署理湯漢樞機日前發表家書、不點名批評有神父發表「含沙射影或煽動仇恨及引致社會動盪的誹謗和冒犯性言論」，要求神父講道時避談政治事件。教會沒有因打壓而自我噤聲，有教會神父今日（30日）主持彌撒時繼續談及政治，形容1997年主權移交時，由香港改變中國的幻想已破滅，嘆香港漸變成中國集權統治下的一個城市。"},{"pid":"77cd1a1a33cdd4276d1019f37c2ad267262b1453","tid":2181051,"uid":362346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T10:19:21.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"8610be9da6df2ba25a3f7d5922a839e8a3a2e548","tid":2181051,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77cd1a1a33cdd4276d1019f37c2ad267262b1453","tid":2181051,"uid":362346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T10:19:21.000Z","msg":"ok"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T10:20:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"165976c7404205e9019f1716